            . I am in partnership with 
               <persName id="t18131027-65-person696">
                  George 
                  Levi
               <interp inst="t18131027-65-person696" type="surname" value="Levi"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18131027-65-person696" type="given" value="George"></interp>
